      "para_id": "Q001557.2",
      "line_range": "2",
      "translation": "(ii 1) ... from the temple of the personal god .... May ..., Nanše , the lady of boundarieṣ Ninĝirsu , the king of weaponṣ Ĝatumdug , the mother of Lagaš , Ig-alima , the beloved šhild of Ninĝirsu , ..., and seat another man on his throne ! May they put an end to his lineage ! May they make his name disappear !"
    }
  ],
